Microsoft Office 365 A1 Plan with 1 TB One Drive cloud storage free for Educational Use! 
1. Go to <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/education/products/office">Office 365</a>
2. Enter your university email (uits edu mail) in the school email field and click on 'GET STARTED'. In that case your email address would be [your id / roll@uits.edu.bd].
3. Click on 'I'm a student'.
4. Provide your additional valid personal information and the verification code that would be sent to your uits edu mail.
5. Click on 'Start'.

Done! Now enjoy free 1 TB one drive cloud storage with Microsoft Office 365 A1 Plan.
